title: LOOKing for many Scrims! :)))) HELP US!
body:
Hi we are looking for Scrims **(Platin - Diamond)** to finish our Tryout process. We play every day in the following days till Friday next week! Support us and pick a Date you wish to play (19:00 best of 3)

Pick a date as long as they are hot. they are gone faster than warm bread!! :D
